---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import InlinePill from "../components/InlinePill.astro";
import profileImage from "../assets/me-again.jpg";
import sandwichPressImage from "../assets/breville.png";  
import crystalPalaceImage from "../assets/crystal-palace.png";
---

<Layout title="About - Steve Whitfield">
  <main class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="text-center mb-16">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-teal-700 dark:text-teal-400 mb-4">About Me</h1>
      <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-teal-600 dark:bg-teal-500 mx-auto"></div>
    </section>

    <!-- Profile Section -->
    <section class="mb-20">
      <div
        class="max-w-5xl mx-auto bg-gray-100 dark:bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-white/10 p-8"
      >
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-start">
          <!-- Profile Image -->
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <img
              src={profileImage.src}
              alt="Steve Whitfield"
              class="w-64 h-64 object-cover rounded-lg border-2 border-teal-600 dark:border-teal-500/30"
            />
          </div>

          <!-- Profile Text -->
          <div class="flex-1 text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-white/90 leading-relaxed">
            <p class="mb-4">
              Hello, I'm Steve â€” Father of two & co-founder of <InlinePill
                href="https://ludi.co"
                icon="image"
                iconSrc="https://ludi.co/favicon.ico">Ludi.co</InlinePill
              >. I'm 38 years old. My favourite color is <InlinePill
                href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Teal"
                icon="color"
                iconColor="bg-teal-500">teal</InlinePill
              > and my favourite dinosaur is <InlinePill
                href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ankylosaurus"
                icon="emoji"
                iconEmoji="ðŸ¦•">Ankylosaurus</InlinePill
              >.
            </p>
            <p class="mb-4"> I pretend to support 
              <InlinePill
                href="https://www.cpfc.co.uk/"
                icon="emoji"
                iconEmoji="âš½">
                Crystal Palace FC
              </InlinePill>
              but really I don't care about football.
            </p>
              <p class="mb-4">
              My bad habits are biting my nails, and cooking oven food on a 
              <InlinePill
                href="https://www.google.com/search?sca_esv=c5f5a1ac408d1a38&sxsrf=AE3TifNGfdY15otYiHppgNSpFsblwYi4XQ:1761748958953&udm=2&fbs=AIIjpHxU7SXXniUZfeShr2fp4giZ1Y6MJ25_tmWITc7uy4KIeioyp3OhN11EY0n5qfq-zEMZldv_eRjZ2XLYc5GnVnMEtRJH_E5imJ0re0I8RdIGDibzfi3DVjoCZDEtNCbl43pLHAxglF9NvaLrxE6qjO4hvt2df8Xmknu_rm0Wna_uIOxUZcq2AfNCiVgxuZi8BdVx_AJi87mWnNGOufqkEOi-L8Omhg&q=Breville+sandwich+press&sa=X&sqi=2&ved=2ahUKEwiN4Ian0smQAxVa2gIHHdDvCY4QtKgLegQIDxAB&biw=1948&bih=1049&dpr=1"
                icon="image"
                iconSrc={sandwichPressImage.src}
                >Breville sandwich press</InlinePill
              > when I want a snack.  Honestly, you can cook hash browns from frozen in under 5 minutes!
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Life Story Section -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-teal-700 dark:text-teal-400 mb-4">My Life Story</h2>
        <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-teal-600 dark:bg-teal-500 mb-8"></div>

        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-white/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          I was born on 20th August 1987 in Rotherham, South Yorkshire.
          Rotherham is very nice, you should go.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-white/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          On my 3rd birthday I ran away from my parents and their friends
          singing Happy Birthday to me and locked myself in my grandparents
          caravan.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-white/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          As a child I enjoyed sailing, computer games and collecting rare milk
          bottle tops. One of those is a lie but I only had two things and three
          is better.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-white/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          I didn't really enjoy school, and ended leaving with average grades
          and average memories.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-white/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          I attended Nottingham Trent University, completed a placement at
          Hewlett Packard in Germany, and graduated with a 1st class degree in
          Software Engineering. Overall, university was good.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-white/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          From 2009 to 2016, I worked the following jobs:
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="my-4 mb-8">
        <div class="overflow-x-auto">
          <table
            class="min-w-full border border-gray-300 dark:border-white/10 text-gray-700 dark:text-white/80 text-left rounded-lg overflow-hidden"
          >
            <thead class="bg-teal-600 dark:bg-teal-600/60 text-white">
              <tr>
                <th class="py-2 px-3 font-semibold">Dates</th>
                <th class="py-2 px-3 font-semibold">Company</th>
                <th class="py-2 px-3 font-semibold">Role</th>
                <th class="py-2 px-3 font-semibold">Notes</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr class="odd:bg-gray-50 dark:odd:bg-white/5 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-white/10 transition">
                <td class="py-2 px-3">2009â€“2010</td>
                <td class="py-2 px-3">Esendex</td>
                <td class="py-2 px-3">Junior Developer</td>
                <td class="py-2 px-3">Decent</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="odd:bg-gray-50 dark:odd:bg-white/5 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-white/10 transition">
                <td class="py-2 px-3">2010â€“2011</td>
                <td class="py-2 px-3">Omnifone</td>
                <td class="py-2 px-3">Software Developer</td>
                <td class="py-2 px-3">Chaos (bad kind)</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="odd:bg-gray-50 dark:odd:bg-white/5 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-white/10 transition">
                <td class="py-2 px-3">2011</td>
                <td class="py-2 px-3">TTT Money Corporation</td>
                <td class="py-2 px-3">Software Developer</td>
                <td class="py-2 px-3">Awful</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="odd:bg-gray-50 dark:odd:bg-white/5 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-white/10 transition">
                <td class="py-2 px-3">2011â€“2014</td>
                <td class="py-2 px-3">Crab Creative</td>
                <td class="py-2 px-3">Web Developer</td>
                <td class="py-2 px-3">Chaos (good kind)</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="odd:bg-gray-50 dark:odd:bg-white/5 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-white/10 transition">
                <td class="py-2 px-3">2014â€“2016</td>
                <td class="py-2 px-3">Chelsea Apps</td>
                <td class="py-2 px-3">Software Engineer & Tech Lead</td>
                <td class="py-2 px-3">Lucrative</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-white/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          In 2016, myself and 4 others left Chelsea Apps and took our Large
          Global Accounting Firm client with us. We setup our own consultancy
          and were paid handsomley for our work from 2016 until 2019.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-white/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          In early 2019, we wound up the consultancy and, later on that year, I
          launched the first version of Metro Retro.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-white/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          In 2017 I get engaged to the love of my life.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-white/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          A year later, Covid-19 caused the popularity of Metro Retro to
          skyrocket. Jamie Hanratty joins as our co-founder.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-white/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Two years later (which is WAY too long), Metro Retro took it's first
          paying customers.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-white/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          After scrapping for another two years, Metro Retro joins TinySeed.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-white/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          In 2025, Metro Retro rebrands as Ludi.co
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-white/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Also in 2025, I decide to make a personal website, I'll let you know
          how it turns out.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
